<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī Āṁjanēyasvāmiki 
<lb n="2"/>svasti śrī vijayābhyuda 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ya śālivāhana śaka 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>varṣaṁbbulu 1662 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="5"/>Aguneṭi śithātti nāma saṁ 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vvatsara kārttika śu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>lu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> takkeḷapā 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍu Aṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ga bhuvi śa <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>purapu Agrahāra <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>lonu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> nityanaivēdhya dī<unclear>pā</unclear> 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>rādhanaku naḍiceṭaṭugānu 
<lb n="12"/>rājaśrī kānugōhi śivarā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="13"/>niṁgāru śelavu yiccina mānyaṁ 
<lb n="14"/>400 kuṁṭala prāptini 785 <unclear>pā</unclear> 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>parakā Aravīsamu śalavu yisti 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>mi ganuka Ācaṁdrārkasthāyigā 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>nu naḍipiṁcagalavāramu yiṁ 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>duku hadulu tūrpu gūḍaveṁkka 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ṭabhaṭlu cēnu paḍumaṭa gēṭu dakṣiṇāni 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ki ḍoṁka paḍamaṭiki ḍoṁka Uttarā 
<lb n="21" break="no"/>naku nārāyaṇaṁ vāri celānuṁcci 
<lb n="22"/>vaccē kāluva <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattā dviguṇaṁ 
<lb n="23"/>puṇyaṁ paradattāna pāla 
<lb n="24" break="no"/>naṁ paradattāpahārēṇa svadattā ni 
<lb n="25" break="no"/>ṣphalaṁ bhavēt <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīrāmā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
